00:09:20,837 --> 00:09:25,883
I just noticed that you are eating your breakfast and reading a newspaper.

84
00:09:26,943 --> 00:09:29,527
He says, when I'm eating breakfast, I'm eating breakfast.

85
00:09:29,567 --> 00:09:31,489
When I'm eating the newspaper, I'm reading the newspaper.

86
00:09:33,551 --> 00:09:35,673
See, it depends where you put your attention.

87
00:09:36,514 --> 00:09:46,403
So when you're at work or when you're doing something, make sure you have the right intention for doing this particular piece of work.

88
00:09:46,604 --> 00:09:50,827
