89
00:09:52,090 --> 00:09:54,351
And then you put your attention into what you're doing.

90
00:09:54,673 --> 00:10:00,860
Now, in our meditation, we've found this place of an objective observer.

91
00:10:01,419 --> 00:10:07,586
So there's this feeling of a self looking at, this feeling of an observer looking at things.

92
00:10:07,606 --> 00:10:09,288
Now that's actually a false place.

93
00:10:09,349 --> 00:10:11,350
It's not the final end that we want to get to.

94
00:10:12,091 --> 00:10:14,735
But then we think that's what we've got to do in daily life.

95
00:10:14,754 --> 00:10:19,379
